Multicenter analysis of long-term oncologic outcomes of hepatectomy for elderly 
patients with hepatocellular carcinoma.

Xing H(1), Liang L(1), Wang H(2), Zhou YH(3), Pei YL(4), Li C(1), Zeng YY(5), Gu 
WM(6), Chen TH(7), Li J(8), Zhang YM(9), Wang MD(1), Zhang WG(4), Pawlik TM(10), 
